# ⚡ DevPulse — GitHub Analytics Dashboard

A full-stack web application that provides detailed analytics for any GitHub user including repository stats, language distribution, and top repositories.

## 🔗 Live Demo
👉 https://devpulse-tau-olive.vercel.app

## 📸 Features
- 🔍 Search any GitHub username
- 📊 View total repos, stars and forks
- 🧑‍💻 Language distribution pie chart
- 🏆 Top repositories by stars
- 📍 Profile info with location and bio

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
**Frontend:** React.js, Recharts, Axios, Vite

**Backend:** Python, FastAPI, Uvicorn

**API:** GitHub REST API

**Deployment:** Vercel (frontend) + Render (backend)

## 🚀 How It Works
1. User enters any GitHub username
2. React frontend calls FastAPI backend
3. Backend fetches data from GitHub REST API
4. Data is aggregated and sent back to frontend
5. Dashboard renders charts and stats

